
# Repository Code Owners
# These users/teams will be requested for review when changes are made to specified paths

# Global owners for any file not specifically covered
* @ops-team @security-team

# Workflow and CI/CD changes require security review
.github/workflows/ @security-team @devops-leads
.github/ @security-team @devops-leads

# Infrastructure and deployment changes
playbooks/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team
inventories/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team
roles/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team
group_vars/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team
host_vars/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team

# Security-sensitive files
vault.yml @security-team
**/vault*.yml @security-team
**/secrets*.yml @security-team
ansible.cfg @ops-team @security-team

# Scripts and automation
scripts/ @ops-team @automation-team
Makefile @ops-team @automation-team

# Documentation requires technical writing review
docs/ @ops-team @tech-writing-team
README.md @ops-team @tech-writing-team
*.md @tech-writing-team

# Configuration and templates
templates/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team
files/ @ops-team @infrastructure-team

# Monitoring and observability
**/monitoring/ @ops-team @sre-team
**/prometheus/ @sre-team
**/grafana/ @sre-team

# Release and deployment procedures
docs/release/ @ops-team @release-managers
scripts/evidence/ @ops-team @release-managers
scripts/rollback/ @ops-team @security-team @release-managers

# Archive cleanup and maintenance (security-sensitive)
scripts/maintenance/ @ops-team @security-team

# Golden path tests and validation
tests/ @ops-team @qa-team
scripts/monitoring/ @ops-team @sre-team

# Root configuration files
/.* @ops-team @security-team
requirements.yml @ops-team
